00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:17.660
Sometimes you find some unusual way that animal
life can exist there

00:10:17.660 --> 00:10:25.350
but virtually no people at all.
This is the Antarctic coast near the Dry Valleys.

00:10:25.350 --> 00:10:30.570
It's perma frost.
