00:10:30.570 --> 00:10:40.290
And this is the Niger River in northern Mali.
In the middle foreground is a mosque.

00:10:40.290 --> 00:10:44.110
It's taken during the flood season when everybody's
growing rice.

00:10:44.110 --> 00:10:50.110
And this is, uh, the north side of the Himalaya
in the Qaidam

00:10:50.110 --> 00:10:56.470
Basin in China.
