It's an old, umm, lake deposit.
When you have really severe rains from one

00:11:38.990 --> 00:11:42.000
direction it's kinda like
sandblasting soft wood.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:45.310
You get these kind of fluted ridges that pop
up and this is an area

00:11:45.310 --> 00:11:49.240
that's, umm, frequented by heroin smugglers
