00:11:49.240 --> 00:11:53.650
the desert without being seen and it was very
hard to get the Iranian

00:11:53.650 --> 00:11:56.410
military police to take me out there because
they were worried about

00:11:56.410 --> 00:11:57.410
getting shot.
Let alone having the crazy American taking

00:11:57.410 --> 00:11:58.410
pictures of their terrain.
Got arrested three times over there.

00:11:58.410 --> 00:12:06.010
Umm, this is out in the Altiplano in Bolivia.
This is edible salt being harvested for human

00:12:06.010 --> 00:12:14.639
consumption.
And this is also in Iran in the salt deserts.

00:12:14.639 --> 00:12:20.589
Lake Tashk.
Home to a lot of flamingos.

